{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"contains","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/contains","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p><code>contains</code> 関数は、第 1 引数の文字列に第 2 引数の文字列が含まれているかどうかを判定し、真偽値 true または false を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".e6.a7.8b.e6.96.87","title":"構文","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">contains(<em>haystack</em> ,<em>needle</em> )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".e5.bc.95.e6.95.b0","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"haystack\"><code><em>haystack</em></code></dt>\n <dd>検索される文字列</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"needle\"><code><em>needle</em></code></dt>\n <dd><code><em>haystack</em></code> の部分文字列かどうかを検索する文字列</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".e6.88.bb.e3.82.8a.e5.80.a4","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code><em>haystack</em></code> に <code><em>needle</em></code> が含まれていれば <code>true</code>。 そうでなければ <code>false</code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".e5.ae.9a.e7.be.a9","title":"定義","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-contains\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.2</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_.e3.81.a7.e3.81.ae.e3.82.b5.e3.83.9d.e3.83.bc.e3.83.88","title":"Gecko でのサポート","isH3":true,"content":"<p>サポート済み。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"contains 関数は、第 1 引数の文字列に第 2 引数の文字列が含まれているかどうかを判定し、真偽値 true または false を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"contains","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"contains","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"contains","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"contains","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"contains","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/xpath/functions/contains","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/xpath/functions/contains/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/contains","title":"contains"}],"pageTitle":"contains - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}